{
  "stem": "1918.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as they had done so many times before, by the morning, they changed orders, and they did not take us to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us to-- on another transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they piled us into an ice cold train, one car of which was heated for the fat SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were fat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of them were so fat sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- yeah, the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS who accompanied us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were eating and drinking in the heated car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were in an ice cold train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know how long we rode, but we arrived somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we arrived, they peeled us off the cattle car, and they put us in-- and-- and they took us to some kind of an-- a clearing, a green clearing in a forest.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they piled us onto open tractors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we saw the Nazis busily running about getting shovels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that of course meant that we are going to dig our own graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, this time, it wasn't that either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The shovels were for digging ditches, tank traps against the Russians, which we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they took us to another part of the forest, where they had 10 what they called, telts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Wooden, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] umbrella-like structures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Paper thin wood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And each-- each one had hundred prisoners, and they piled us into those 10 structures.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And every morning, they took us out the other end of the forest, marching through the town, where the traffic had to be stopped.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And children were going to school, and people were going to work, and fresh bread from bakeries, and the smell of food of all kinds.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a town called, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And today they say the length and breadth of Germany was filled these camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
